[p 
	"Cowlitz Gamers 2nd Adventure is a platformer where you must collect all the gold nuggets to advance to the next stage. This run uses 2 players to beat the game as fast as possible.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Emulator Used: BizHawk 2.3.1 with NESHawk core.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Aside from routing, death warps and frame perfect rope grabs are the most important ways to save time on this game. Also hit detection is only processed every other frame (alternating per player) so this is used to duck under certain enemies and quickly keep moving. 
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"This is a several second improvement over my last WIP. Seeing as no improvements were forthcoming from anyone else, I decided to go back and give a final look at the second half of the game before submitting, as I don't like having unfinished projects. It's funny how many things you notice after a while of not looking at something.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Special thanks to FractalFusion for pointing out a secret square that opens a faster route in one level.
]p
